description: Magnificent Custom-Modern home. NOW COMPLETED!! This home features huge custom made windows on the front allowing tons of natural light to flow into the home. Brazilian Mahogany front door with German hardware. CEDAR SIDING (A NATURAL TERMITE REPELLANT) wrapping all around the home. Kitchen features mocha brown shaker cabinets complimented with butcher block countertop. Both bathrooms feature walk-in rain showers, imported tile from Spain, premium navy vanities with calacatta quartz, gold hardware and plumbing fixtures. Located in the heart of Dallas. Minutes from Deep Ellum, Downtown and Uptown. MUST SEE THIS DALLAS GEM!!!

description: Stunning modern new construction designed to impress with remarkable attention to detail. Great quality finish-out and gorgeous open concept with split bedrooms. Upon entering this breathtaking home you'll be in awe of the vaulted entryway, extensive wood-like laminate floors and decorative lightning throughout. Chef's kitchen with stunning granite counter-tops, custom cabinetry and a sweeping island over looks the sophisticated dining room and elegant living room with decorative electric fireplace and a wall of windows with park and trail views. Serene master suite boasts a separate shower, large tub, dual sink and spacious walk-in closet. This home is convenient to public parks, schools, hospitals, shopping centers, Dart station, freeways and just 15 minutes away from Downtown Dallas.

description: Remodeled 4 bed, 2 bath home includes a custom mudroom & utility room. This home is in a wonderful location, with walking distance to local dining, shopping, and schools with quick access to I-635, 175, & 20. The flow of this floor plan & its oversized covered patio makes this home ideal for entertainment. Updated kitchen includes SS appliances, quartz countertops & backsplash. Both bathrooms have also been updated. Other upgrades include LVP flooring throughout common areas, carpet in the bedrooms, fresh paint, lighting fixtures, & electric fireplace. Foundation was corrected in August 2021 with transferable warranty, HVAC has been serviced and all ducts have been replaced, & 75% of the electrical has been updated including a new panel box. The exterior of the home has also been painted, front porch resurfaced & new sbs wood fence has been installed.

description: Enjoy superb living at this incredible location just steps away from Downtown Dallas, parks, golf courses and access to major highways. Entering this open floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, you are greeted with crisply painted interior, decorative lighting, hardwood floors, mosaic stone encased fireplace and an abundance of natural light. Updated eat-in kitchen is fit with custom wood cabinets, breakfast-bar island, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and opens to the spacious living and dining room. Light adorns the master bedroom which boasts an ensuite bath and walk-in closet. The fourth bedroom serves as the perfect guest bedroom complimented by an en-suite bath and walk-in closet. Don't miss the sizable 23x27 garage! Relax, cookout, entertain in the expansive backyard and enjoy convenient living near White Rock Lake and Dallas Arboretum. See 3D Tour for more details!

description: Commanding 1.3 acre gated estate features an 18,769 SF main house. Originally designed by Robbie Fusch, then reimagined and transformed by the current owner. This stunning home includes a 7000 SF addition! With light, bright living spaces, 7 bedrooms all vying to be the primary, a 2,026 SF climate-controlled auto showroom. The terraced backyard with infinity-edge pool, sunken fire pit and outdoor kitchen, overlooks Bachman Branch. Notable highlights: Lutron Smart Home system, elevator, Venetian plaster walls, catering kitchen, media room, tasting room with kitchen and chilled storage for approx. 1,000 bottles, exercise, spa, beauty room, billiard room, blue Agate bar, backup generator, and so much more.

You'll be greeted by large trees, fresh landscaping & all new exterior paint, leading you to an arched entryway. All one story, the living & dining room are perfect for a quiet afternoon & large enough for gathering with friends & family, with bonus room functioning as a nursery abutting the space. Kitchen includes quartz countertops, timeless white backsplash, stainless steel appliances, laundry, room for a breakfast table & a doorway to the back patio, yard & detached garage. The master bedroom includes two separate walk-in closets, & an en-suite filled with natural light, dual sinks, garden tub, & separate shower.

description: Light, bright European style Modern Mediterranean estate in PH. Impressively appointed soaring 2 story ceilings downstairs frame picturesque pool views. All of the rooms down wrap around the pool & backyard & give access to the outdoors. White kitchen, dual dishwashers, new countertops & equipment. Multiple bar areas throughout, Bev fridges, wine fridges, ice prep sinks. Large quarters attached to house has a full kitchen, dining, large living & full bath plus a media room & is also all on the ground floor. Recently build large Pool Cabana has a large entertaining space, full kitchen + dual sliding doors that open to the pool deck & make it perfect for entertaining & maximizing the living experience. 1st floor large laundry & huge side yard-storage that runs the length of the house & is perfect for stashing or setup with entertainment or gardens. 4 car garage & storage plus two guest beds upstairs each with private baths & another large living area. Steps from CM, shopping & dining.

description: Stunning Lake Highlands traditional home situated on corner hill w mature trees & beautiful landscaping. Gorgeous formal living room invites guests into bright room w walls of windows, wood flooring, WBFP w wet bar. Adjoining updated kitchen has soapstone counters, glass backsplash, SS Bosch appliances w large prep Island, adjoining breakfast & dining rooms. First floor master retreat is generous in size, raised ceiling, bay window & adjoining bath w dual vanities, soaking tub, shower & two closets. Home has 4 additional bedrooms served by 2 baths. Downstairs media room is perfect spot for entertaining. Open courtyard patio leads to pool w spa & larger back lawn w fire pit, b-o-b fencing & mature trees to the West.

description: A must-see Prairie home in Historic Munger Place with an abundance of character and a long list of upgrades for modern living! Expansive covered front porch, rooms reconfigured to provide a spacious floor plan with well thought-out finishing touches, 10-foot ceilings, original hardwoods and stained glass, an abundance of windows, updated kitchen with granite and stainless appliances, refreshed bathrooms, two staircases, electronic privacy gate, detached two-car garage, and new turf in backyard. Come see this elegant blend of old and new before its gone! A list of upgrades will be provided.

description: MOVE-IN READY!! Beautifully updated mid century craftsman located in the heart of Historic Lake Cliff and within minutes from Bishop Arts District. This well maintained property offers designer touches throughout and features an open concept family area, study, and formal dining room adjacent to the beautifully updated galley style kitchen. Enjoy the calming water views from your living area or take a stroll around the Historic Lake Cliff Park just steps away from front porch. This home boasts two large bedrooms, one half bath, and two full baths highlighted by a spa like owners retreat with ensuite and dual vanities and walk in custom closet. This property is all about Location, Location, Location so bring your pickiest buyers!
